  "content": {
    "problemStatement": "### **Aptitude Practice Question**\n\nThe student was expelled from the university due to his flagrant violation of the rules and regulations.\n\n(a) Blatant\u00a0\n(b) Inconspicuous\u00a0\n(c) Secretive\u00a0\n(d) Obvious\n\n---\n\n### **Answer & Explanation**\n\nBlatant",
